Prepare forcing data from ERA5

1. Download the ERA5 with CDS API ==  "ERA5 download"
   1) prepare the CDS API script
   2) submit the script to cluster

2. Check the downloading file == "ERA5 merged"
   1) check the downloading time period == "sis_check_ERA5"
   2) merge + seldate + sellonlat + interpolated (CDO script) == "sis_check_ERA5"
